# odoodev-gui v1.3.0 | tauri (react + rust)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
▸ Install:  pnpm install
▸ Dev:      pnpm tauri dev
▸ Build:    pnpm tauri build          # needs TAURI_SIGNING_PRIVATE_KEY (updater)
▸ Check:    pnpm tauri build --no-bundle   # compile-check, no signing
▸ Front:    pnpm run typecheck && pnpm run lint
▸ Rust:     cd src-tauri && cargo fmt && cargo clippy && cargo test
▸ Release:  bump version → git tag vX.Y.Z → git push upstream vX.Y.Z
▸ CI:       gh run list --repo equitania/odoodev-gui
▸ Linux:    curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/equitania/odoodev-gui/main/install.sh | bash
            # install.sh: apt (.deb) on Debian/Ubuntu, AppImage elsewhere; re-run = update
